## Article 7. Storage and Management of Information

The Developer will endeavor to implement reasonable and appropriate security measures to prevent unauthorized access, leakage, loss, destruction, alteration, or other improper handling of user information.

Information collected by third-party service providers will be managed in accordance with the privacy policies, terms of service, and information management practices of the relevant third-party service providers.

## Article 8. Retention Period

Collected information will be retained only for the period necessary to achieve the purposes for which it was collected, for the period required by applicable laws or regulations, or for the period specified by the relevant third-party service provider.

After the applicable retention period has expired, the information will be deleted or anonymized by reasonable means.

## Article 9. Use by Children

Where the App is provided to or intended for use by children, the Developer will endeavor to ensure that children’s information is handled appropriately in accordance with applicable laws and Google Play policies.

Parents and legal guardians are responsible for reviewing this Policy and the content of the App and for providing appropriate supervision when a child uses the App.

