To the extent provided under applicable laws, users may have the right to request access to, correction of, deletion of, or restriction of the use of information relating to them.

However, the Developer may be unable to respond to such requests where the Developer does not retain information that directly identifies the user or where the relevant information is held solely by a third-party service provider.

